(6934, 3151, 837, 3, 'Lumi Pumpuli', '2008年4月，林笛拥有一只可爱的小猫，10天后死于传染性腹膜炎，林笛创作此歌纪念这只叫做Lumi Punpuli的小猫。\r\nLumi Pumpuli 芬兰语意为雪棉花球', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'Lumi Pumpuli\r\n\r\nonce upon a time, \r\nin the first blush of spring, \r\na tiny snowflake fell from heaven. \r\nwhen this magical snowflake landed on earth \r\nshe melted into the form of a white kitten. \r\neveryone who saw her was instantly charmed. \r\neven people on the other side of the world \r\n\r\nWho named her Lumi Pumpuli,\r\nWho feed her milk and fish\r\nwho built a little bed for her to sleep\r\nwho held her in their hand, \r\nwho felt happy ''cause she is purring\r\nwho laughed when she looked silly\r\nsuch was love''s design\r\n\r\n\r\nBut springtime snows do not last \r\nLumi had to return to heaven. \r\nwhen the tiny snowflake melted, \r\nshe left behind a pool of tears. \r\n\r\nlumi - wait for me in heaven\r\nmami will be there soon\r\nthere''s a tiny bright star in the night sky\r\nto the right of the lonesome moon\r\n\r\nLumi, Lumi are you there somewhere?\r\nLumi, Lumi can you come back home?\r\n\r\nLumi lumi wait for me in heaven\r\nLumi mami will be there soon\r\nthere''s a tiny bright star in the night sky\r\nshining to me like tear drops.\r\n\r\nWho can no longer call Lumi Pumpuli,\r\nwho can never touch little fish bowl?\r\nWho buried a little body under a tree\r\nWho won''t need to clean the paw print\r\nWho can’t smile at her pictures\r\nWho''s open eyes saw sun turn black\r\nwas such love''s design?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLumi Pumpuli on the way to heaven,\r\nwill she miss everything used to be given?\r\nIf there is no milk, fish, hug and kiss\r\nwill you run back to mami’s dream?\r\n\r\nclimb my leg,\r\npurr in my lap, \r\nlay by my head \r\nrolling by my side\r\njump on the table\r\nsteal my fish\r\nfollow me everywhere\r\nplay hide and seek\r\n\r\nsuch was love''s design\r\n', '', 303, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-14 20:33:00', '2013-10-07 17:12:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6935, 3151, 837, 1, 'Perfect Ghost I', 'Perfect Ghost ', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'I would like to be a falling cloud \r\nLanding gently by your side\r\nThe slightest wisp melted by your body heat.\r\n\r\nI would like to be the stars that you can see \r\nAny leaf you can hold in your mouth\r\nAny stone you can put in your pocket\r\nAny one you can meet on the street\r\n\r\nSince you walked into my secret garden\r\nI have become all too real\r\nIt seems I will never disappear\r\nI can come alive in anything\r\n\r\nI am the only god of my own world\r\ncrying in my cage day and night\r\nEvery day you save me on the brink of collapse\r\nEvery day you kiss my numb and frozen face\r\n\r\nOh, my perfect ghost\r\nNightly meet in a perfect dream\r\nOh, my perfect ghost\r\nAppear in the silent mirror\r\n\r\n\r\nSince you walked into my secret garden\r\nI have become all too real\r\nIt seems I will never disappear\r\nI can come alive in anything\r\n\r\n\r\nThis world is just as big as two hearts\r\nOne stops beating, and the other would die\r\nThis is the most beautiful result I believe\r\nStaring into each other''s dying eyes\r\n', '', 241, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-14 20:40:03', '2013-10-07 17:12:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(6936, 3151, 837, 2, 'Perfect Ghost II', 'Perfect Ghost', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'The roses you send still smell fragrant\r\nEven if withered… \r\nYou disappear for a while the world become stifling\r\nI am like a child abandoned in the desert of white\r\nWhat do I have to be proud of?\r\nI am just a lonely soul\r\n\r\nEven if you surround me with praise everyday\r\nI still hang in an endless void\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nAlone I sleep\r\nAlone I awake\r\nI do not know the meaning of life\r\nWithout you somewhere waiting\r\n\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nAlone I sleep\r\nAlone I awake\r\nI do not know the meaning of life\r\nWithout you somewhere waiting\r\n', '', 225, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-14 20:46:58', '2013-10-07 17:12:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
